headline: CDW (CDW) Fell as Market Yet to Accept it as an “AI Winner”
summary: Wedgewood Partners, an investment management company, released its third-quarter 2025 investor letter. The letter is available for download here. AI stocks remain the favorite topic of Wall Street in the third quarter.
